      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that gets the job done? This car is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone needing dependable transportation at a great value. It's ready to take you on your next adventure!",
