    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a solid choice for someone looking for a project or a budget-friendly daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a few minor dents. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to ensure long-term reliability. It\u2019s an honest car that needs a little TLC to get back to its best.",
