    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, currently maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits no discernible wear, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies the most exacting requirements of a discerning collector. From its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments, every detail remains as precise as the day of its manufacture. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an automobile of unrivaled caliber and mechanical integrity.",
