    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained since day one. This car is in absolute pristine condition, having been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed to preserve its mirror-like finish. The exterior is free of any stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, protected by a high-end ceramic coating that makes the deep metallic paint pop under any lighting. Step inside to an interior that still carries that new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and every electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively through authorized dealerships. It drives tight, smooth, and powerful, with no leaks, rattles, or deferred maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been pampered by a single enthusiast owner. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a detailed service log.",
